text: Hybolasius trigonellaris is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Hutton in 1898. It is known from New Zealand.BioLib.cz - Hybolasius trigonellaris. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1898
